title: The God-Emperor delivers again
author: VD
content_html: Amy Coney Barrett has been confirmed by the Senate as a U.S. Supreme Court Justice, 53-46. She may not be ideal, but she’s almost certain to be much, much better than the late, unlamented Ruth Bader Ginsberg.
